# ğŸ›¡ï¸ SafeMe

**SafeMe** is a one-command Linux server security tool that automates critical hardening tasks such as setting up firewalls, securing SSH access, mitigating DDoS attacks, monitoring file integrity, and locking down kernel-level network configurations â€” all via a simple CLI or Python API.

